"title": "4040: beauty",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4040: beauty",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A physical or spiritual quality which brings pleasure to those who behold it. Scripture stresses the beauty of God himself and his creation, while noting that the beauty of the creation can lead away from God or become idolised.</p>\n<h2>Beauty in nature</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:31\">JOB 38:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:21\">GEN 49:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:6\">EZK 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:7-Ezek31:9\">EZK 31:7–31:9</a></p>\n<h2>Beautiful people</h2>\n<h3>Women</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:17\">GEN 29:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:11\">EST 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:2\">GEN 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:11\">GEN 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:14\">GEN 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:15-Gen24:16\">GEN 24:15–24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:7\">GEN 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:11\">DEU 21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:3\">1SA 25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:1\">2SA 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:27\">2SA 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:3-1Kgs1:4\">1KI 1:3–1:4</a>EST <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:7\">2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:15\">JOB 42:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:11\">PSA 45:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:14\">SNG 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:7\">SNG 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:1\">SNG 7:1</a></p>\n<h3>Men</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:6\">GEN 39:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:12\">1SA 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:42\">1SA 17:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:25\">2SA 14:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:6\">1KI 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:16\">SNG 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:10\">SNG 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:6\">EZK 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:23\">EZK 23:23</a></p>\n<h3>An enhanced quality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:2-Esth2:3\">EST 2:2–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:9\">EST 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:12\">EST 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:24\">ISA 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:20\">EZK 7:20</a></p>\n<h3>Beauty and lack of beauty as external impressions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:2\">ISA 53:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:22\">PRO 11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:30\">PRO 31:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:3\">1PE 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>May lead to pride and lust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:25-Prov6:26\">PRO 6:25–6:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:17\">EZK 28:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:11-Gen12:12\">GEN 12:11–12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:7\">GEN 39:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:4\">2SA 11:2–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:12\">EZK 23:12</a></p>\n<h2>Beautiful artefacts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:5\">LUK 21:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21\">JOS 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:3-Ezek27:4\">EZK 27:3–27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:11\">EZK 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:24\">EZK 27:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:2\">ACT 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>The beauty of Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:2\">PSA 50:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:2\">PSA 48:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:2\">JER 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:15\">LAM 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10-Ezek16:15\">EZK 16:10–16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:25\">EZK 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:45\">DAN 11:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h2>The beauty of God as the joy of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:2\">ISA 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:5\">ISA 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:17\">ISA 33:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:3\">ISA 61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:16\">JER 11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:15\">ROM 10:15</a></p>",
